<li sourcefile="articles/finance/cost-accounting/tasks/create-assign-cost-behavior-policy-cost-control-unit.md" sourcestartlinenumber="81">In the Cost object dimension hierarchy node field, enter or select a value.
<ul sourcefile="articles/finance/cost-accounting/tasks/create-assign-cost-behavior-policy-cost-control-unit.md" sourcestartlinenumber="82">
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/cost-accounting/tasks/create-assign-cost-behavior-policy-cost-control-unit.md" sourcestartlinenumber="82">By default, the variable percentage is 100 percent.</li>
