<li sourcefile="articles/finance/cost-accounting/tasks/create-assign-cost-behavior-policy-cost-control-unit.md" sourcestartlinenumber="83">Click Policy assignments for cost control unit.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/cost-accounting/tasks/create-assign-cost-behavior-policy-cost-control-unit.md" sourcestartlinenumber="84">Click New.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/cost-accounting/tasks/create-assign-cost-behavior-policy-cost-control-unit.md" sourcestartlinenumber="85">In the list, mark the selected row.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/cost-accounting/tasks/create-assign-cost-behavior-policy-cost-control-unit.md" sourcestartlinenumber="86">In the Valid from accounting date field, enter a date.
<ul sourcefile="articles/finance/cost-accounting/tasks/create-assign-cost-behavior-policy-cost-control-unit.md" sourcestartlinenumber="87">
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/cost-accounting/tasks/create-assign-cost-behavior-policy-cost-control-unit.md" sourcestartlinenumber="87">The rules are date-effective, and a user or the system can expire a rule if a newer version is created.</li>
